  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Resilience. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.2KVllUXqgWq7jCmX]{Sanguine Tenacity}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Survival checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.49y9Ec4bDii8pcD3]{Subsist}. At 17th level, if you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Vk7BzAb3D9r226sI]{Legendary Guide}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Ta61ObC8Lk7BxTFO]{Legendary Survivalist}, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
